data.description: Discover your next home in this impeccably well maintained 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 car garage beauty.  Offering a Modern open floorplan concept, with a spacious Kitchen and great room for entertaining. Kitchen offers Tons of cabinets, nice pantry, and center Island. This home boasts a fabulous back yard with Southern exposure and views of Peavine Mountain from the patio.  Also, the terraced hillside is perfect for fruit tree's and a garden. Pride of ownership shows here!
